    <div class="step-instructions screensteps-textblock screensteps-wrapper--introduction screensteps-wrapper">
  <div id="text-content_377c7ba7-2689-41e3-b9c2-a0c33416f351" class="text-block-content">
    <p>If enabled by your institution, you can use Announcements Redesign to provide an enhanced experience for course announcements. When enabled in your course, Announcements Redesign displays for all announcements and all users in your course.</p>
<p>Announcements Redesign is currently a <a href="/t5/Instructor-Guide/How-do-I-manage-feature-options-for-a-course/ta-p/710" target="_blank">feature option</a>. </p>
<p><strong>Note: </strong>If Announcements Redesign is not available in your course, it has not been enabled by your institution.</p>
  </div>
</div>

      <div class="step screensteps-section screensteps-depth-1" id="enable-feature-option" data-step-uuid="fa34dbb8-b78d-4361-af3f-5b1d0b2ce9d3">
    <h2 id="enable-feature-option" class="step-title screensteps-heading">Enable Feature Option</h2>
      <div class="step-instructions screensteps-textblock">
  <div id="text-content_86babbee-8514-4a46-991b-a76ff2005f8d" class="text-block-content">
    <p>In order to use Announcements Redesign in your course, you first need to enable the feature option from Course Settings. If the feature option is not available, it has not been enabled by your institution.</p>
  </div>
</div>
 
        <div class="step screensteps-section screensteps-depth-2" id="open-feature-options" data-step-uuid="0f4ed6ad-69b9-4492-afe5-105ae8b517ce">
    <h3 id="open-feature-options" class="step-title screensteps-heading">Open Feature Options</h3>
        <div class="image screensteps-image">
      <img src="https://media.screensteps.com/image_assets/assets/008/168/031/original/53d61f62-f56d-44b9-8e67-06800273535e.png" srcset="" alt="Open Feature Options" height="798" width="824">
  </div>
 
      <div class="step-instructions screensteps-textblock">
  <div id="text-content_b0dd2483-23d9-4095-9923-a3cf3157f1ad" class="text-block-content">
    <p>In Course Navigation, click the <strong>Settings</strong> link [1]. Then click the <strong>Feature Options</strong> tab [2].</p>
  </div>
</div>
 
  </div>
 
        <div class="step screensteps-section screensteps-depth-2" id="enable-discussions-redesign" data-step-uuid="76bc3f76-16c8-4b5e-b852-6e407d8dbd6a">
    <h3 id="enable-discussions-redesign" class="step-title screensteps-heading">Enable Discussions/Announcements Redesign</h3>
        <div class="image screensteps-image">
      <a href="https://media.screensteps.com/image_assets/assets/008/168/035/original/6b8d313a-20fa-4dec-961e-946b7b409523.png" class="screensteps-image-zoom" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener noreferrer">
        <img src="https://media.screensteps.com/image_assets/assets/008/168/035/medium/6b8d313a-20fa-4dec-961e-946b7b409523.png" srcset="" alt="Enable Discussions/Announcements Redesign" height="490" width="855">
      </a>
  </div>
 
      <div class="step-instructions screensteps-textblock">
  <div id="text-content_6f42422b-f6c6-49f6-95e4-51d1d6130455" class="text-block-content">
    <p>Locate the <strong>Discussions/Announcements Redesign</strong> feature [1] and click the <strong>State</strong> icon so it displays as enabled [2].</p>
<p>Learn more about <a href="/t5/Instructor-Guide/How-do-I-manage-feature-options-for-a-course/ta-p/710" target="_blank">managing feature previews in your course</a>.</p>
<p><strong>Note:</strong> If the feature is not available, it has not been enabled by your institution. Contact your Canvas administrator for assistance.</p>
  </div>
</div>
 
  </div>
 
  </div>

      <div class="step screensteps-section screensteps-depth-1" id="open-announcements" data-step-uuid="efbd8b0e-99ab-45c4-b440-ae8f2c067972">
    <h2 id="open-announcements" class="step-title screensteps-heading">Open Announcements</h2>
        <div class="image screensteps-image">
      <img src="https://media.screensteps.com/image_assets/assets/008/536/978/original/6930dc99-2100-4244-a5d5-dcb191df3850.png" srcset="" alt="Open Announcements" height="312" width="176">
  </div>
 
      <div class="step-instructions screensteps-textblock">
  <div id="text-content_8c2c0560-dfc5-4bdf-a6bd-4f4b459bc5bb" class="text-block-content">
    <p><span style="color:rgb(38,38,38);">In Course Navigation, click the <strong>Announcements</strong> link.</span></p>
  </div>
</div>
 
  </div>

      <div class="step screensteps-section screensteps-depth-1" id="open-discussion" data-step-uuid="55f7ced9-d6b8-4c4a-ade0-321a160c7d52">
    <h2 id="open-discussion" class="step-title screensteps-heading">Open Announcement</h2>
        <div class="image screensteps-image">
      <a href="https://media.screensteps.com/image_assets/assets/008/536/980/original/30931ae3-fc28-4a37-9070-40e61a7d99e0.png" class="screensteps-image-zoom" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener noreferrer">
        <img src="https://media.screensteps.com/image_assets/assets/008/536/980/medium/30931ae3-fc28-4a37-9070-40e61a7d99e0.png" srcset="" alt="Open Announcement" height="446" width="855">
      </a>
  </div>
 
      <div class="step-instructions screensteps-textblock">
  <div id="text-content_488961a2-577b-4416-a494-dbc480356ba3" class="text-block-content">
    <p>To view an announcement in the Announcements Redesign interface, click the name of the announcement [1].</p>
<p>Learn more about how to <a href="/t5/Instructor-Guide/How-do-I-use-the-Assignments-Index-Page/ta-p/777" target="_blank">use the Assignment Index page</a>.</p>
  </div>
</div>
 
  </div>

      <div class="step screensteps-section screensteps-depth-1" id="view_discussion" data-step-uuid="d314cd3d-34e4-4225-9660-fc63edee6e22">
    <h2 id="view_discussion" class="step-title screensteps-heading">View Announcement</h2>
        <div class="image screensteps-image">
      <a href="https://media.screensteps.com/image_assets/assets/008/168/039/original/7bc39a81-2d53-4a94-ac66-9da16fcb6fe8.png" class="screensteps-image-zoom" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener noreferrer">
        <img src="https://media.screensteps.com/image_assets/assets/008/168/039/medium/7bc39a81-2d53-4a94-ac66-9da16fcb6fe8.png" srcset="" alt="View Announcement" height="632" width="855">
      </a>
  </div>
 
      <div class="step-instructions screensteps-textblock">
  <div id="text-content_105d2d59-382a-42b4-977a-4764008947db" class="text-block-content">
    <p>An announcement displayed in the Announcements Redesign interface includes three sections: the announcement toolbar [1], announcement [2], and announcement replies [3].Â </p>
  </div>
</div>
 
        <div class="step screensteps-section screensteps-depth-2" id="view-discussion-toolbar" data-step-uuid="379edf52-fb14-4368-8155-4532ac05ca8f">
    <h3 id="view-discussion-toolbar" class="step-title screensteps-heading">View Announcement Toolbar</h3>
        <div class="image screensteps-image">
      <img src="https://media.screensteps.com/image_assets/assets/008/168/042/original/d1b74fb4-860c-4a4a-9ca7-321c98c2b5bc.png" srcset="" alt="View Announcement Toolbar" height="222" width="853">
  </div>
 
      <div class="step-instructions screensteps-textblock">
  <div id="text-content_ed926f8c-eacd-40ad-9b4b-51635aa0bbff" class="text-block-content">
    <p>To search for replies or specific authors, enter your terms in the search field [1].</p>
<p>To filter replies, click the <strong>Filter </strong>drop-down menu [2]. You can filter by all replies or unread replies.</p>
<p>To sort replies by newest or oldest, click the <strong>Sort </strong>button [3].</p>
<p>To view threaded replies in a split screen sidebar, click the <strong>View Split Screen </strong>button [4].</p>
<p>To view threaded replies all at once, click the <strong>Expand Threads </strong>button [5]. You can collapse the threaded replies by clicking the <strong>Collapse Threads </strong>button [6].</p>
<p>To view threaded replies inline, click the <strong>View Inline </strong>button [7].</p>
  </div>
</div>
 
  </div>
 
        <div class="step screensteps-section screensteps-depth-2" id="view-discussion-topic" data-step-uuid="f49eb36e-0ee9-4427-920a-d12a8389e5be">
    <h3 id="view-discussion-topic" class="step-title screensteps-heading">View Announcement Topic</h3>
        <div class="image screensteps-image">
      <a href="https://media.screensteps.com/image_assets/assets/008/168/046/original/65b83d16-a371-49c2-b063-f6e2bd98917b.png" class="screensteps-image-zoom" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener noreferrer">
        <img src="https://media.screensteps.com/image_assets/assets/008/168/046/medium/65b83d16-a371-49c2-b063-f6e2bd98917b.png" srcset="" alt="View Announcement Topic" height="381" width="855">
      </a>
  </div>
 
      <div class="step-instructions screensteps-textblock">
  <div id="text-content_2d847bd8-db7d-4130-87c4-586cb9f77095" class="text-block-content">
    <p>The announcement topic section includes important information about the announcement, including the topic title [1] and description [2].</p>
<p>You can also view the name of the author [3], the role of the author [4], the date and time the announcement was published [5] or edited [6], and number of replies [7].</p>
  </div>
</div>
 
  </div>
 
        <div class="step screensteps-section screensteps-depth-2" id="view-discussion-options" data-step-uuid="d90920d6-8137-40ff-97c3-ab5795255fba">
    <h3 id="view-discussion-options" class="step-title screensteps-heading">View Announcement Options</h3>
        <div class="image screensteps-image">
      <a href="https://media.screensteps.com/image_assets/assets/008/536/982/original/c025fe95-10c0-4b47-b54f-67766951d741.png" class="screensteps-image-zoom" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener noreferrer">
        <img src="https://media.screensteps.com/image_assets/assets/008/536/982/medium/c025fe95-10c0-4b47-b54f-67766951d741.png" srcset="" alt="" height="362" width="855">
      </a>
  </div>
 
      <div class="step-instructions screensteps-textblock">
  <div id="text-content_9e70beae-0f26-488c-bedb-1206c2966ba6" class="text-block-content">
    <p>The announcement topic section also includes several tools that allow you to manage your announcement.</p>
<p>To subscribe to or unsubscribe from the announcement, click the <strong>Subscribe</strong> icon [1].</p>
<p>To open the announcement's Options menu, click the <strong>Options</strong> icon [2]. Use the links in the Options menu for the following:</p>
<ul>
<li>To mark all replies as read, click the <strong>Mark All as Read</strong> link [3]. </li>
<li>To mark all replies as unread, click the <strong>Mark All as Unread</strong> link [4].</li>
<li>To <a href="/t5/Instructor-Guide/How-do-I-edit-an-announcement-in-a-course/ta-p/1190" target="_blank">edit announcement details</a>, click the <strong>Edit</strong> link [5]. </li>
<li>To <a href="/t5/Instructor-Guide/How-do-I-delete-an-announcement-in-a-course/ta-p/1200" target="_blank">delete the announcement</a>, click the <strong>Delete</strong> link [6].</li>
<li>To <a href="/t5/Instructor-Guide/How-do-I-send-an-announcement-to-another-instructor/ta-p/887" target="_blank">send the announcement to another instructor</a>, click the <strong>Sent To...</strong> link [7]. </li>
<li>To <a href="/t5/Instructor-Guide/How-do-I-copy-an-announcement-to-another-course/ta-p/888" target="_blank">copy the announcement to another course</a>, click the <strong>Copy To... </strong>link [8].</li>
</ul>
  </div>
</div>
 
  </div>
 
  </div>

      <div class="step screensteps-section screensteps-depth-1" id="view-discussion-replies" data-step-uuid="9e178f08-6f8f-4659-96d3-0665e1db2b12">
    <h2 id="view-discussion-replies" class="step-title screensteps-heading">View Announcement Replies</h2>
        <div class="image screensteps-image">
      <a href="https://media.screensteps.com/image_assets/assets/008/168/051/original/b87c1480-e381-4319-b069-d1937af81208.png" class="screensteps-image-zoom" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener noreferrer">
        <img src="https://media.screensteps.com/image_assets/assets/008/168/051/medium/b87c1480-e381-4319-b069-d1937af81208.png" srcset="" alt="View Announcement Replies" height="670" width="855">
      </a>
  </div>
 
      <div class="step-instructions screensteps-textblock">
  <div id="text-content_6d800f15-366d-46d0-b09a-3d79517f26fe" class="text-block-content">
    <p>Announcement replies display below the announcement topic [1]. </p>
<p>To <a href="/t5/Instructor-Guide/How-do-I-view-a-thread-in-Announcements-Redesign-as-an/ta-p/485662" target="_blank">view threaded replies</a>, click the <strong># of replies</strong> link [2]. </p>
<p>Learn how to <a href="/t5/Instructor-Guide/How-do-I-reply-to-an-announcement-in-Announcements-Redesign-as/ta-p/478620" target="_blank">reply to an announcement</a> and <a href="/t5/Instructor-Guide/How-do-I-view-and-sort-announcement-replies-in-Announcements/ta-p/478616" target="_blank">view and sort announcement replies</a>.</p>
  </div>
</div>
 
  </div>

      <div class="step screensteps-section screensteps-depth-1" id="view-rich-content-editor" data-step-uuid="3435863d-4802-48ce-8dbd-2def3b3e2a1a">
    <h2 id="view-rich-content-editor" class="step-title screensteps-heading">View Rich Content Editor</h2>
        <div class="image screensteps-image">
      <img src="https://media.screensteps.com/image_assets/assets/008/536/985/original/38875805-8665-478e-a5a5-f0241b8c2589.png" srcset="" alt="View Rich Content Editor" height="425" width="769">
  </div>
 
      <div class="step-instructions screensteps-textblock">
  <div id="text-content_ec6cb31d-20b5-4bf7-86c4-7a55aaeeec97" class="text-block-content">
    <p>When creating or editing announcement topics or replies, you enter and edit your content using the Rich Content Editor. The Rich Content Editor allows you to format text, link text to course or external content, insert media, attach files, and <a href="/t5/Instructor-Guide/How-do-I-mention-a-user-in-an-announcement-reply-in/ta-p/485661" target="_blank">@mention course users</a>. <a href="https://community.canvaslms.com/t5/Instructor-Guide/tkb-p/Instructor#RichContentEditor" target="_blank">Learn more about using the Rich Content Editor.</a></p>
  </div>
</div>
 
